								<td style="font:14px/21px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#363636;padding:29px 0 13px">
									<b>Hi Anthony,</b><br><br>
									


You now have free access to the course materials!<br><br>

In this class you will learn an important programming technique called Object Oriented Programming. 
This will allow you to share and reuse code almost like Lego blocks.<br>
<br>
But we would be disappointed if that were the only outcome of this course. We want your work to be a 
source of joy for others. In that spirit, we will work together to build 6 projects that will spread 
happiness to those around you.
<br><br>

The course material is open, meaning you can take it at your own pace. So start learning and stay Udacious!
